mixin Tricks()
    section.tricks.container
        h2 How to Master English Quickly
        p Here are some expert tips to help you learn English efficiently:
        ul.tricks__list
            li.tricks__item Practice every day &ndash; Consistency is key to making progress.
            li.tricks__item Immerse yourself &ndash; Listen to English podcasts, watch movies, and speak whenever you can.
            li.tricks__item Use language apps &ndash; Reinforce what you learn with interactive tools.
            li.tricks__item Take small steps &ndash; Focus on one lesson at a time for the best results.
            li.tricks__item With the right approach, anyone can become fluent in English, no matter their starting point!